Titolo: Angry Birds Fight!

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: Angry Birds Fight! was a match-3 puzzle video game with role-playing game elements and was the eleventh installment in the Angry Birds series. The game was co-developed by Rovio Entertainment and Kiteretsu Inc. The game was soft-launched in some Asian Pacific countries in early 2015 and the worldwide release was on June 11, 2015. In the game the player must match enough Angry Birds to earn enough power to defeat the enemy players and pigs. It was called a combination of Candy Crush (another mobile game) and RPG gaming.On August 1, 2017, the game was removed from the Play Store and App Store with the game's servers permanently shutting down by that November.